The paper deals with optimization problems related to learning on graphs and hypergraphs, which are common topics in machine learning and data science. The paper also mentions applications in graph-based semi-supervised learning and PageRank, which are specific areas of interest in the field of artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
